## What formats of session data can I use?
You can type notes directly, paste in a transcript, or upload audio for transcription (coming soon). All of this is linked to the client's profile and active goals.

## Is this just for athletic coaches?
Not at all. While congenial-carnival supports athletic training, it's equally useful for executive coaching, creative mentorship, academic advising, or any other long-term support role.

## Is client data secure?
Yes. congenial-carnival uses encryption at rest and in transit. We follow best practices for handling personal data, and we're committed to transparency and control for both coaches and clients.
